gnutls_x509_crt_check_email(3)                                                                    gnutls                                                                    gnutls_x509_crt_check_email(3)

NAME
       gnutls_x509_crt_check_email - API function

SYNOPSIS
       #include <gnutls/x509.h>

       unsigned gnutls_x509_crt_check_email(gnutls_x509_crt_t cert, const char * email, unsigned int flags);

ARGUMENTS
       gnutls_x509_crt_t cert
                   should contain an gnutls_x509_crt_t type

       const char * email
                   A null terminated string that contains an email address (RFC822)

       unsigned int flags
                   should be zero

DESCRIPTION
       This function will check if the given certificate's subject matches the given email address.

RETURNS
       non-zero for a successful match, and zero on failure.

REPORTING BUGS
       Report bugs to <bugs@gnutls.org>.
       Home page: https://www.gnutls.org

